{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}
{% block title %}LensPkr Rules{% endblock %}

{% block body %}
<main class="rules">
    <h1>LensPkr Privacy Policy</h1>
    <span>Last updated: {{ now|date('d/m/Y') }} </span>
    <h2>Welcome to LensPkr. Protecting your privacy is important to us. This privacy policy explains what information we collect, how we use it and what your rights are.</h2>
    <h3>1. Data collected</h3>
    <ul>We collect the following types of data:</ul>
        <li>- Account information : Last name, first name, e-mail address, password.</li>
        <li>- Browsing information : IP address, device type, pages viewed.</li>
        <li>- User content**: Messages, publications, comments and other interactions on the platform.</li>
    <h3>2. How we use your data</h3>
    <ul>We use your data to:</ul>
    <li>- Manage your account and provide you with our services.</li>
    <li>- Improve and personalize your experience on LensPkr.</li>
    <li>- Ensure the security of the platform and prevent abuse.</li>
    <li>- Communicate with you regarding updates or offers related to LensPkr.</li>
    <h3>3. Data sharing</h3>
    <ul>Your data will not be sold. It may be shared with :</ul>
    <li>- Our service providers (e.g. hosting, analytics) as part of our operations.</li>
    <li>- Legal authorities in the event of a legal obligation.</li>
    <h3>4. Data security</h3>
    <li>We implement security measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, loss or alteration.</li>
    <h3>5. Your rights</h3>
    <ul>In accordance with current regulations, you have the right to:</ul>
    <li>- Access your personal data.</li>
    <li>- Rectify, delete or limit the processing of your personal data.</li>
    <li>- Withdraw your consent for certain uses.</li>
    <li>- File a complaint with the competent authorities.</li>
    <h3>6. Cookies and similar technologies</h3>
    <li>We use cookies to improve your browsing experience and analyze platform usage. You can manage your preferences via your browser settings.</li>
    <h3>7. Policy changes</h3>
    <li>This policy may be updated. We will inform you of any significant changes.</li>
    <li>If you have any questions, please contact us at LensPkr@gmail.com.</li>
    <li>Thank you for using LensPkr with confidence!</li>
</main>
{% endblock %}

